frames.caption: A mysterious figure in an intricately designed hooded cloak stands in a dark, enchanted forest. They hold a fiery, glowing flower, casting an ethereal light around them. The cloak is adorned with ornate patterns and a skull emblem, adding to the mystical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark, magical forest filled with blooming flowers. The central figure, cloaked in a detailed garment, holds a flower that appears to be on fire, illuminating the surroundings with a warm glow.

frames.caption: A mysterious figure in an ornate hooded cloak stands amidst a dark forest, holding a flaming flower. The cloak is intricately designed with golden patterns and a skull motif, adding to the enigmatic atmosphere. Flames dance around the figure, casting a warm glow against the somber backdrop.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark, mystical forest where a lone figure holds a flower engulfed in flames. The ornate cloak and surrounding fire create a sense of magic and mystery.
